{"tid":343942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好屈中共呀！中共從來冇講過一地兩檢係唯一方案呀！","createTime":"2017-08-02T01:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T03:02:25.000Z","uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f43403a6be3f75cb5b2b9ecf889ce18a3f1e8d0","tid":343942,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T01:34:04.000Z","msg":"這幾天在深圳，當然要做實地調查啦，而且要幫中共平反呀！真㗎！話說香港政府強推一地兩檢，仲要話從來冇考慮第二方案，嗱！嗱！嗱！唔好屈中共呀！中共從來冇講過一地兩檢係唯一方案呀！係你林鄭將啲說話塞落人哋把口咋！我去到福田高鐵站，中共喺幾層預留極極極極極極極大量空間，俾兩地兩檢， 由等候區、到安檢區、到出入境區&hellip;&hellip;都預留晒土地！ 大家所見到我拍嘅空間係真相嘅十份一！我從來未見過任何一個機場、火車站、陸空海管制區係大到咁！中共係預咗你兩地兩檢的！甚至有執法人員同我講，其實仲可以由福田高鐵站整個通往「市民中心站」嘅大型隧道都可以改變成另一個安檢區！尼次我幫大陸呀！應付8萬？18萬？每日人流綽綽有餘啦！<br />\nps. 袁生林太，人哋預咗 兩地兩檢，就唔好將啲地租畀人哋唔該！<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CHANWANHOI/posts/1617375758304552?hc_location=ufi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCHANWANHOI%2Fposts%2F1617375758304552%3Fhc_location%3Dufi&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e2f1ffa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CHANWANHOI/posts/1617375758304552?hc_location=ufi</a>"},{"pid":"0293e43cc5a88d807f6ba0d4fae56b4ab50ccedc","tid":343942,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T01:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20376082_1617374988304629_4915997429401100735_n.jpg?oh=f334a75f3cc7e18790d1d6c678bcdf32&amp;oe=5A384EEE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20376082_1617374988304629_4915997429401100735_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df334a75f3cc7e18790d1d6c678bcdf32%26oe%3D5A384EEE&h=ad178024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20430155_1617375031637958_332048053011129648_n.jpg?oh=d28a8fa1aeceea4a6d9f0c10f1e13311&amp;oe=5A3265A4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20430155_1617375031637958_332048053011129648